Task
Maximum array element
Write a function maxInArray that takes arr as an argument and returns the maximum element in the array.
Use a loop in your solution. The use of the Math.max () method is not permitted.
Example:
• function maxInArray ([3, 4, 8, 1]) must return 8;
• function maxInArray ([11, 12) must return 12;
• function maxInArray ([1, 1]) must return 1;
• the maxInArray ([]) function must return undefined.

Solution
function maxInArray (arr) {
   let max = arr [0];
   if (arr.length === 0) return undefined;
     for (let i = 1; i <arr.length; i ++) {
       if (arr [i]> max) {
       max = arr [i];
       }
     }
     return max;
}
